{
  "stem": "13096.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were just [? hurting. ?] And I mean, tell you about the-- the beds, how horrible they were.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were, you know, four-- four planks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Four planks with no nails or nothing, going like, four nails, how you put it in the table.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the four nails, you know, they had three layers of planks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One layers, the plank's going the-- you know? and-- and that-- in that piece of wood, they were laying some planks like what, you know, from here.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like you say, call it two meters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On top, there was another layers, the same thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then top-- at third floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the-- in each one-- in each one layer there, we have to sleep, 12 people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But even if you put, you know, one next to the other one, you will never fit in two meters three-- 12 bodies.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it means to say, we were all-- we were without even blankets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were all in the same direction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If during the night, you know, you are tired of sleeping in one side, and we want turn to the other side, they would say, girls, can we turn?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of the 12 people would turn the other side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if you take the one person sleeping one direction, and one into the other side, we will never fit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So much-- so much we were moving and making noise and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they hoped that it was just, you know, to make us, you know, demoralized.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The whole thing will collapse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because there were no nails.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the 14 people in there first, the second, and the third, we found ourself all on the floor with the planks around us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we will start all over again, making our bed, putting the four planks together.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
